title: Pagano has to ask himself some hard questions
text: > Top News Pagano has to ask himself some hard questions FILE- In this Oct. 18, 2015, file photo, Indianapolis Colts wide receiver Griff Whalen (17) watches as Indianapolis Colts free safety Colt Anderson (32) is tackled New England Patriots running back James White (28) on a punt in the second half of an NFL football game in Indianapolis. The Colts (3-3) were giving the Patriots (6-0) a good game when they handed Tom Brady and Bill Belichick the victory Sunday night with an ill-conceived fake punt attempt on fourth-and-3 from their own 37. (AP Photo/AJ Mast, File)
